### Feature Flag System API Test Requests

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Get All Feature Flags
GET http://localhost:5000/api/feature-flags

### Get Feature Flag by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/feature-flags/1

### Get Feature Flag by Name
GET http://localhost:5000/api/feature-flags/by-name/OpenBankingPilot

### Create New Feature Flag
POST http://localhost:5000/api/feature-flags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "TestFeature",
  "description": "Test özelliği",
  "isEnabled": true,
  "createdBy": "test-user"
}

### Update Feature Flag
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/feature-flags/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Güncellenmiş açıklama",
  "isEnabled": true,
  "updatedBy": "test-user"
}

### Check Feature Flag - Success Case
POST http://localhost:5000/api/feature-flags/validation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "featureName": "OpenBankingPilot",
  "userIdentifier": "CUST001",
  "userType": "Customer",
  "appVersion": "1.2.0"
}

### Check Feature Flag - Not in Pilot
POST http://localhost:5000/api/feature-flags/validation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "featureName": "OpenBankingPilot",
  "userIdentifier": "CUST999",
  "userType": "Customer",
  "appVersion": "1.2.0"
}

### Check Feature Flag - Version Too Low
POST http://localhost:5000/api/feature-flags/validation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "featureName": "OpenBankingPilot",
  "userIdentifier": "CUST001",
  "userType": "Customer",
  "appVersion": "1.0.0"
}

### Check Multiple Feature Flags
POST http://localhost:5000/api/feature-flags/validation/batch
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "featureName": "OpenBankingPilot",
    "userIdentifier": "CUST001",
    "userType": "Customer",
    "appVersion": "1.2.0"
  },
  {
    "featureName": "SealPilot",
    "userIdentifier": "CUST002",
    "userType": "Customer",
    "appVersion": "1.1.0"
  },
  {
    "featureName": "SoftLoginPilot",
    "userIdentifier": "EMP001",
    "userType": "Employee",
    "appVersion": "1.0.0"
  }
]

### Get Pilot Whitelist for Feature Flag
GET http://localhost:5000/api/feature-flags/1/pilot-whitelist

### Add User to Pilot Whitelist
POST http://localhost:5000/api/feature-flags/pilot-whitelist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "featureFlagId": 1,
  "userIdentifier": "CUST003",
  "userType": "Customer",
  "minVersion": "1.1.0",
  "expiresAt": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "createdBy": "admin"
}

### Refresh Cache
POST http://localhost:5000/api/feature-flags/cache

### Delete Feature Flag
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/feature-flags/5

### Remove from Pilot Whitelist
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/feature-flags/pilot-whitelist/4

